Steven Jay "Steve" Cohen (born August 29, 1955 in Chicago, Illinois) was a member of the 1988 Olympic Judo team for the United States and the coach of the Olympic team in 2000. He competed in the 95kg division. Earlier in his career, Cohen won the bronze medal in the -80kg division at the 1975 Pan American Games.Cohen's brother Irwin and two nephews Aaron  and Richard are all accomplished judoka.


